            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Silvano <lb n="2"/><supplied reason="lost">D</supplied>eo <expan><abbr>Domes</abbr><ex>tico</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/><supplied reason="lost">s</supplied>olvit sa<lb break="no" n="4"/>crum <lb n="5"/>libe<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr></expan> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> V<lb break="no" n="6"/>eturius <lb n="7"/>Titianus <lb n="8"/>b<expan><ex>ene</ex><abbr>f</abbr><ex>iciarius</ex></expan> co<expan><ex>n</ex><abbr>s</abbr><ex>ularis</ex></expan>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. Unregelmäßige, unterschiedlich hohe Zeilen. Stellenweise kaum noch lesbar. (B): Kremer: Z. 2: [--]o. AE 1903: Z. 8: F, aber in der Auflösung richtig: b(ene)f(iciarius).</p>
            </div>
